       <article class="post-2 page type-page status-publish hentry" id="post-2">
        <header class="entry-header">
         <div class="entry-header-inner">
          <h1 class="entry-title">
           Home
          </h1>
         </div>
         <!-- .entry-header-inner -->
        </header>
        <!-- .entry-header -->
        <div class="entry-content">
         <p>
          <a href="https://allerton.csl.illinois.edu/files/2018/03/Allerton-Conf-website-graphic.jpg">
           <img alt="" class="wp-image-1550 aligncenter" height="582" sizes="(max-width: 1164px) 100vw, 1164px" src="https://allerton.csl.illinois.edu/files/2018/03/Allerton-Conf-website-graphic-300x150.jpg" srcset="https://allerton.csl.illinois.edu/files/2018/03/Allerton-Conf-website-graphic-300x150.jpg 300w, https://allerton.csl.illinois.edu/files/2018/03/Allerton-Conf-website-graphic-768x384.jpg 768w, https://allerton.csl.illinois.edu/files/2018/03/Allerton-Conf-website-graphic-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https://allerton.csl.illinois.edu/files/2018/03/Allerton-Conf-website-graphic.jpg 1200w" width="1164"/>
          </a>
         </p>
         <h2>
          56th Annual Allerton Conference on Communication, Control, and Computing
         </h2>
         <p>
          <strong>
           Hosted by the Coordinated Science Laboratory at the University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign
          </strong>
         </p>
         <p>
          Each year, the Allerton Conference draws some of the brightest minds from industry, academia and government to discuss innovation in the fields of communication, control and computing. We invite you to submit your work and join us at Allerton Park and Retreat Center for an exciting few days of presentations, special events and networking.
         </p>
         <h3>
          <strong>
           October 2, 2018
          </strong>
         </h3>
         <p>
          <a href="https://allerton.csl.illinois.edu/opening-tutorials/">
           Opening Tutorial Sessions
          </a>
          , given by
          <strong>
           Paulo Tabuada
          </strong>
          , UCLA and
          <strong>
           João Hespanha
          </strong>
          , UCSB
          <br/>
          <a href="http://csl.illinois.edu/about/directions">
           Coordinated Science Laboratory
          </a>
          , CSL Auditorium (B02), 1308 West Main Street, Urbana, IL
         </p>
         <h3>
          <strong>
           October 3-5, 2018
          </strong>
         </h3>
         <p>
          Main Conference and
          <a href="https://allerton.csl.illinois.edu/2015-conference/plenary-talk/">
           Plenary Lecture
          </a>
          , given by
          <strong>
           Professor A. Stephen Morse
          </strong>
          , Yale University on Thursday, October 4, 4:00-5:00pm
          <br/>
          <a href="http://allerton.illinois.edu">
           Allerton Park and Retreat Center
          </a>
          , 515 Old Timber Road, Monticello, IL
         </p>
         <p>
          <strong>
           2018 Conference Co-Chairs: Negar Kiyavash and Daniel Liberzon
          </strong>
         </p>
        </div>
        <!-- .entry-content -->
       </article>
       <!-- #post-## -->
